728822f-a.title: Richmond: Fingerboard Road - Columbia Avenue
728822f-a.text:
Fingerboard Road, south side, between Columbia Ave. and Cleveland
Place. Bromley's 1917 map shows the hoase to have belonged to E.G.
Anderson.
June 29, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
